videos.description: Johnny Davis picks off the pass then flies towards the rim for the one-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Johnny Davis gets the steal and jam for Wisconsin) 2021/12/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnny Davis gets the steal and jam for Wisconsin

videos.description: Michael Devoe shakes the defender and hits the three. Then Wisconsin's Johnny Davis knocks down the tough 3-pointer right before the halftime buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Devoe, Davis exchange impressive 3s to end the half) 2021/12/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Devoe, Davis exchange impressive 3s to end the half

videos.description: Brad Davison forces a Georgia Tech timeout as he scores 9  straight for Wisconsin.

videos.headline: Davison rips off 9 points himself

videos.description: Brad Davison tries to save the ball, but ends up taking out a fan and spilling a drink.

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Jordan Usher has a good look at a 3-pointer, but he comes up short as Wisconsin hits a few free throws and pulls out the win.
